# Tower of Hanoi

Tower of Hanoi is a classic puzzle. You have 3 towers and 3 discs on first tower. The object of the puzzle is to move all 3 discs from first tower to last tower

## Rules

You canâ€™t place a larger disc on smaller disk. It may seem a bit simple at first, but go ahead and try it with 3, 4, 5 discs.

